Yet Another Gears OpenGL demo
-----------------------------

The yagears package contains a version of the popular gears OpenGL demo
that supports multiple graphic renderers:
  - GLX interface (OpenGL Extension to the X Window System)
  - DirectFBGL interface (OpenGL Extension for DirectFB)
  - GLFBDev interface (OpenGL Extension to the Linux Framebuffer)
  - EGL interface with X11 display
  - EGL interface with DirectFB display
  - EGL interface with Linux Framebuffer display

Have fun,

Nicolas Caramelli
